{"tid":1854584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(不死亞視)將派20萬個口罩予港人同捐一千萬港幣給武漢作抗疫之用","createTime":"2020-01-31T14:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T16:08:16.000Z","uid":150979,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d76415638262f80f9faf8f6bde6dd5a63a63b8","tid":1854584,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6N8idi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6N8idi.jpg&h=8336a16c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如今口罩在香港市場供應短缺，好多香港人為了買得一盒口罩而通宵排隊，近日剛上任亞洲心動娛樂副總裁的林文龍就為大家帶來好消息。林文龍於亞視的新春團拜活動時表示將會搜羅20萬個口罩派給香港人，以解決現時口罩短缺問題。<br />\n<br />\n林文龍表示知道香港人缺口罩，所以亞視非執行董事兼聯席主席賴彩雲賴主席於馬來西亞搜羅20萬個口罩，希望可以下星期運到香港，解決現時口罩不足問題。另外亦會捐一千萬港幣給武漢作抗疫之用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/209781?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;preview=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F209781%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3Dlink%26preview%3D1&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=8984d8a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/209781?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;preview=1</a>"},{"pid":"854d6829c17396f5fb4f3348fb1545ec0855625c","tid":1854584,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"咁屈機，要撐亞視永恆了"},{"pid":"a1d84cf7accd69d41efbb1a19c775c26b921c72d","tid":1854584,"uid":264245,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:33:07.000Z","msg":"捐1000萬都係唔會比返個電視牌你"},{"pid":"35416789d8107ea273bd1dfc217ab284847243e2","tid":1854584,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/an